It'd be nice to be able to take a project offline, removing the ability for users to update an issues.  This would then allow the currently assigned workflow to the project to be modified without the need to copy / modifiy / migrate it.  Further, it would be nice if you modify a workflow that is currently assigned to an offline project, it would perform the copy / modify / migration behind the scenes, moving to the migration steps when your modifications are complete.  This would reduce the need for JRA-5653

